summary: Changes teeth to white for Khajiit
descriptionHtml:
I was sometimes uneasy about how dull the teeth looked on the Khajiit species, so I simply changed up the brightness a bit so it looks like they have some sort of oral hygiene.
(Who brushes their teeth when theyre an adventurer anyways?)
This is my first texture change and upload since I joined, woo.
author: OutcastKhajiit
